<hymn_number>5254</hymn_number>
<title>hl lqạʾ nḥẓy̱ fyh</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- hal̊ liqāʾuⁿ naḥ̊ẓay̱ fīhi
 biʿarīsinā ạl̊ḥabīb̊
 man̊ ḥayāẗu ạlnãf̊si fīhi
 wah̊wa lil̊qal̊bi niʿ̊ma ạlnãṣīb̊

[V2]
 ạlqrạr: kaẙfa lạa wālrãbũ ṣarãḥ̊
 ạảnãnā maʿ̊hu nakūn̊
 fī dīāri ạl̊maj̊di naf̊raḥ̊
 biạl̊fādī ạảyũhā ạl̊mū̊̉minūn̊

[V3]
 2- kulũnā sẖuk̊raⁿạ nūảdĩy
 bal̊ watar̊tīla ạlsũrūr̊
 ḥaẙtẖu rabũ ạl̊maj̊di yub̊dī
 kulã ḥubiⁿ̃ lidah̊ri ạldũhūr̊

[V4]
 3- ʿan̊ qarībiⁿ naḥ̊nu nub̊ṣir̊
 mā nar̊jūhu biạl̊ʿīān̊
 ại̹dẖ̊ kitābu ạl̊ḥaqĩ yukẖ̊bir̊
 qāyỉlạaⁿ: ại̹nãnā lạ nudān̊</lyrics>
</song>